plot: She-Hulk represents Leap-Frog who was injured due to a malfunction in his custom-made super suit.

Holden assigns Jen the case of Eugene Pastilio, aka Leap-Frog, who is suing Luke for endangerment when Eugenes Leap-Frog costume malfunctions during crimefighting. Luke's lawyer is Matt Murdoch, aka Daredevil, who has been brought in from NYC to help defend Luke in the suit.—Gislef
